Package controllers

Class MainMenu

  • java.lang.Object
    • controllers.MainMenu
  • public class MainMenu
extends java.lang.Object
    MainMenu is a class controlling the selection of games. It interacts with the main menu IO as well as the game template IO to allow the user to select games and users, and displays game windows when they are played.
